data.description: Welcome to Fairview Heights and this special two story with an open floor plan. 5 bedrooms 3 Bathrooms on a quiet culd-e-scac, a gorgeous custom staircase leading up to built in bookshelf that gives the wow factor right when you walk in the front door. This home is great for entertaining with a lovely covered patio and string lights just off of the kitchen, where you can feel like you are in the country and watch the deer on the hill while you have your morning coffee. A half acre lot with tons of landscaping completed leaving it up to the new owners to decide if they'd like grass or xeroscaping (or maybe a combo of both) backs to nature and views. All bedrooms have at least one walk-in closet and ceiling fans with a switch so you don't have to mess with the pull string amid those gorgeous 10 foot ceilings. Master has large walk-in closet, a true 5 piece bath with water closet, shower and soaker spa tub. Full bedroom and full bathroom on main floor make for super comfy guest or mother in law quarters separate from the other 4 bedrooms and 2 full bathrooms upstairs. Got stuff? Welcome to your storage oasis! This home offers tons of attic storage (all easily accessible), plus 2 storage sheds outside and a full storage pantry in the garage to compliment the built in work bench that is full of cabinets and drawers to meet all your storage needs. ** Home is back on market after being professionally cleaned and freshened after client move out. ***
